<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00503</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT STRENGTHENING THE BARANGAY THROUGH SUPPORT FOR BARANGAY OFFICIALS AND VOLUNTEER WORKERS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : Barangay Officials And Volunteer Workers Incentives And Benefits Act Of 1016</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides for the honorarium of one (1) Barangay Health Workers (BHW) and up to twenty (20) Barangay Tanods in each barangay thereby utilizing their Internal Revenue Allotment for the salary of the Punong Barangay and Kagawads, as well as, for Barangay Nutrition Scholars and members of the Lupon ng Tagapamayapa, and for other purposes.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>YAP, VICTOR A.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-06-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Reform</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Catamco (010 2016-08-15)</td><td>2. Panotes (039 2016-10-19)</td><tr><td>3. Espino (047 2016-11-22)</td><td>4. Noel (065 2017-02-01)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON LOCAL GOVERNMENT ON 2016-07-27</td></tr></table>